REQUIREMENTS GATHERING/ANALYSIS

1.Connectivity - 24/7 connectivity
2.Tracking - Tracking trains and which platforms they go through
3.Plotting - Plotting the tracks on map
4.Providing a monitoring interface for the end user - An application with map and overlay of plots with live locations of trains and their routes.
5.An algorithm for better usage of tracks.
6.Budget and time to deliver the product.
7.Assembling a team.

Software requirements:
1.OS: windows, android, IOS.
2.Database: Mongo DB.
